query:
UPDATE
                        occurrences
                    SET
                        skull = $2,
                        amount = $3
                    WHERE
                        id = $1
                    RETURNING
                        id AS "id!: types::OccurrenceId",
                        skull AS "skull: types::SkullId",
                        amount AS "amount: f32",
                        millis AS "millis: types::Millis"
